Class JsonSvgDumper

java.lang.Object
org.krmdemo.techlabs.core.dump.json.JsonSvgDumper
All Implemented Interfaces:
TreeDumper
public class JsonSvgDumper extends Object implements TreeDumper
Implementation of TreeDumper that dumps into the passed PrintStream the tree of a JSON logical structure in SVG-Attrs target format (SVG-Class is coming soon).
